/etc/net 0.5.1
ALTLinux Sisyphus

just apt-get install etcnet and make sure CONFMETHOD in /etc/sysconfig/network
is set to etcnet

Version requirements for /etc/net 0.5.1:
hotplug >= 2004_03_29-alt13 (?)
ifrename >= 28-alt1.pre1
pcmcia-cs >= 3.2.7-alt7
ifplugd >= 0.25-alt3

Note on network-config-subsystem:
/sbin/ifup
/sbin/ifdown
service network
/etc/sysconfig/network
